work_images.title: 002-MacBook-process-wide
work_images.description: Too avoid confusion, the front-end and back-end layouts remained similar. The difference is, a non-member or an un-logged member would see news, tips and links to basic info. After logging in, the user would gain access to a beautiful tiled view of current news, seminars, 100 Grand Winners etc.
